title: Apple, Intel, Tesla, Levi Strauss: What to Watch in the Stock Market Today
sub_head: Apple results are due after the close; Intel’s earnings were down amid a spending uptick
body:
Stock futures edged up as investors considered the speed at which the Federal Reserve would move to lift interest rates, and awaited more earnings from major consumer and technology companies. Here’s what we’re watching in Thursday’s trading:
